00:08:10,270 --> 00:08:13,950
Nothing. They only asked us a few simple questions. It's just a procedure.

125
00:08:13,950 --> 00:08:14,910
I just saw

126
00:08:15,030 --> 00:08:16,320
Big Devil was also inside.

