00:08:16,320 --> 00:08:16,640
Who?

128
00:08:17,360 --> 00:08:18,490
Gu Nanting.

129
00:08:20,370 --> 00:08:21,920
I heard from the Passenger Transport Department that

130
00:08:21,920 --> 00:08:24,750
