132
00:08:28,970 --> 00:08:31,420
Mr. Gu's flight skills are very good.

133
00:08:31,600 --> 00:08:32,120
He is one of the best pilots

134
00:08:32,120 --> 00:08:33,270
in our company.

135
00:08:33,789 --> 00:08:35,350
