221
00:12:17,000 --> 00:12:18,300
We will learn more

222
00:12:18,360 --> 00:12:19,390
and get used to it as soon as possible.

223
00:12:19,390 --> 00:12:20,880
A pilot is the soul of a plane.

224
00:12:20,880 --> 00:12:21,690
Our job

225
00:12:21,720 --> 00:12:22,840
relates to the safety of passengers

226
00:12:22,840 --> 00:12:23,680
and the company's property.

227
00:12:23,680 --> 00:12:25,680
We can't be careless whenever it is.

228
00:12:25,830 --> 00:12:26,830
I agree with that.

229
00:12:27,400 --> 00:12:28,020
However,

230
00:12:28,080 --> 00:12:30,200
I came back from Hokkaido after my vacation last month.

231
00:12:30,200 --> 00:12:32,330
I took the flight XD884 of our company.

232
00:12:32,940 --> 00:12:33,990
For the Captain's Public Address,

233
00:12:33,990 --> 00:12:36,650
