236
00:12:52,680 --> 00:12:53,410
Lin Yicheng.

237
00:12:53,880 --> 00:12:54,430
Mr. Gu.

238
00:12:55,980 --> 00:12:57,000
What was wrong with

239
00:12:57,000 --> 00:12:58,600
the Captain's Public Address during the cruise?

240
00:12:58,600 --> 00:13:00,530
Yes, I was the copilot that day.

241
00:13:01,280 --> 00:13:02,560
Captain Zhang authorized me to do

242
00:13:02,560 --> 00:13:04,290
the Captain's Public Address.

243
00:13:04,390 --> 00:13:06,590
