244
00:13:09,400 --> 00:13:11,900
There was a lack of one public address indeed.

245
00:13:11,900 --> 00:13:13,710
I was not feeling well that day.

246
00:13:14,130 --> 00:13:14,790
I had a cold.

247
00:13:15,500 --> 00:13:16,550
If you fly a plane while having a cold,

248
00:13:16,550 --> 00:13:18,310
