250
00:13:20,470 --> 00:13:21,410
Yes, yes.

251
00:13:23,150 --> 00:13:24,260
I think Cheng Xiao's suggestion

252
00:13:24,260 --> 00:13:25,320
is very good.

253
00:13:25,740 --> 00:13:26,470
Lin Yicheng,

254
00:13:26,640 --> 00:13:29,100
in the future, you must have higher standard

255
00:13:29,200 --> 00:13:30,730
on the details of your work.

256
00:13:31,360 --> 00:13:31,710
Okay.

257
00:13:32,280 --> 00:13:33,270
Don't do it again.

258
00:13:33,270 --> 00:13:33,600
Okay.

259
00:13:35,080 --> 00:13:35,740
Cheng Xiao,

