00:13:37,920 --> 00:13:38,580
is correct.

262
00:13:39,830 --> 00:13:40,560
Lin Yicheng,

263
00:13:41,040 --> 00:13:43,060
Go back and study the operational manual.

264
00:13:43,060 --> 00:13:45,650
Write a self-criticism report with Captain Zhang.

265
00:13:45,650 --> 00:13:46,460
Okay, Mr. Gu.

266
00:13:48,680 --> 00:13:49,380
So, Mr. Gu,

267
00:13:49,960 --> 00:13:52,440
please don't look at me with colored glasses.

268
00:13:52,440 --> 00:13:54,440
And don't doubt my ability in my job.

269
00:13:55,480 --> 00:13:57,760
Ability is the combination of skills and attitude.

270
00:13:57,760 --> 00:13:59,470
Without a serious and modest attitude,

271
00:13:59,470 --> 00:14:00,760
no matter how good your skills are,

272
00:14:00,760 --> 00:14:03,440
you can't guarantee the safety of flight for 100 percent.

273
00:14:03,440 --> 00:14:05,290
Based on your current understanding of this profession,

274
00:14:05,290 --> 00:14:07,280
even if the company lets you to join the Passenger Transport Department,

275
00:14:07,280 --> 00:14:08,940
you must start from working as

276
00:14:09,030 --> 00:14:09,760
an observer.

277
00:14:09,940 --> 00:14:10,920
Observer?

278
00:14:18,510 --> 00:14:19,120
Leaders,

279
00:14:19,520 --> 00:14:21,010
isn't this too unfair?

