She will have to stay in Australia for two months.

566
00:29:07,890 --> 00:29:09,840
What if she is still unqualified in the end?

567
00:29:09,840 --> 00:29:12,370
Then the company's resources will be wasted.

568
00:29:13,220 --> 00:29:14,840
Any potential talent

569
00:29:15,240 --> 00:29:17,240
deserves the company's resources.

570
00:29:23,520 --> 00:29:24,020
Come in.

571
00:29:34,520 --> 00:29:35,120
Mr. Jiang.

572
00:29:39,870 --> 00:29:41,030
Let Mr. Gu tell you.

573
00:29:42,690 --> 00:29:43,350
Cheng Xiao,

574
00:29:44,000 --> 00:29:45,040
from now on,

575
00:29:46,030 --> 00:29:48,200
you are going to prepare for the transition training of 787.

576
00:29:48,200 --> 00:29:50,590
After the training, your post will be determined

577
00:29:50,590 --> 00:29:52,290
according to your performance.

578
00:29:52,290 --> 00:29:53,740
You will give me another test?

579
00:29:53,740 --> 00:29:55,400
What kind of attitude is that?

580
00:29:58,790 --> 00:30:01,520
It's about the company's rules and regulations.

581
00:30:01,550 --> 00:30:04,410
It's not a difficulty created to you deliberately.

582
00:30:05,220 --> 00:30:06,500
It's settled then.

583
00:30:07,070 --> 00:30:08,630
Mr. Gu will be

584
00:30:08,870 --> 00:30:11,930
the full-time instructor for the pilots of your group.

585
00:30:15,700 --> 00:30:16,340
Mr. Jiang,

586
00:30:17,280 --> 00:30:18,950
can we change the instructor?

587
00:30:19,680 --> 00:30:20,290
Why?

588
00:30:21,560 --> 00:30:23,080
Mr. Gu looks young,

589
00:30:23,850 --> 00:30:25,850
but we all know his ability.

590
00:30:27,210 --> 00:30:27,840
However,

591
00:30:28,350 --> 00:30:31,010
we have to thank Nanting fo his coming hard work.

592
00:30:31,840 --> 00:30:33,840
I can only rest assured by handing this group of pilots

593
00:30:33,840 --> 00:30:34,760
to your hands.

594
00:30:36,920 --> 00:30:37,310
Okay.

595
00:30:38,400 --> 00:30:38,960
Sorry.

596
00:30:39,400 --> 00:30:40,660
I have something to do.

597
00:30:40,960 --> 00:30:41,410
So...

598
00:30:42,440 --> 00:30:43,770
Go ahead with your work.

599
00:31:35,030 --> 00:31:36,490
I'll wait for the next one.

600
00:31:46,030 --> 00:31:47,930
I won't give you another chance to get something on me.

601
00:31:47,930 --> 00:31:49,660
See you at the training ground.

602
00:31:51,040 --> 00:31:52,790
You have to keep all the promises

603
00:31:52,790 --> 00:31:53,520
you've made.

604
00:31:53,840 --> 00:31:55,300
Not only will I achieve them all,

605
00:31:55,300 --> 00:31:56,900
I'll also do better than you.

606
00:32:39,100 --> 00:32:39,980
Who is this?

607
00:32:41,000 --> 00:32:41,730
You're back.

608
00:32:42,510 --> 00:32:44,240
How long have you been waiting?

609
00:32:46,440 --> 00:32:49,170
If you didn't show up in 30 minutes, I would leave.

610
00:32:49,550 --> 00:32:51,220
It's worth if if I could make Mr. Gu, who cherishes time

611
00:32:51,220 --> 00:32:52,820
so much, wait for 30 minutes.

612
00:32:54,760 --> 00:32:55,690
Why are you here?

613
00:32:56,440 --> 00:32:58,500
I went to Seattle to study for half a month and I've just been back.

614
00:32:58,500 --> 00:33:00,760
I'm going to make a report to the leaders.

615
00:33:01,030 --> 00:33:02,860
Have you learnt anything from the Boyin headquarters?

616
00:33:02,860 --> 00:33:03,860
I've learnt a lot.

617
00:33:04,320 --> 00:33:07,050
I even went into the general assembly shop of 787.

618
00:33:07,060 --> 00:33:09,430
Recently, to pilot 787, I've always felt that

619
00:33:09,430 --> 00:33:11,560
the automatic push of the engine has changed rapidly.

620
00:33:11,560 --> 00:33:14,360
The stability of the five sides's pitching is low.

621
00:33:14,620 --> 00:33:16,510
I can solve your problem this time.

622
00:33:16,510 --> 00:33:17,900
I'll go back to the cabin to sort out the information,

623
00:33:17,900 --> 00:33:20,030
and send it to your email box tomorrow.

624
00:33:20,630 --> 00:33:22,960
When you're free, let's play basketball.

625
00:33:23,710 --> 00:33:26,240
I'm going to Australia next week. Two months.

626
00:33:27,430 --> 00:33:30,630
Let's make an appointment next time. It's too difficult.

627
00:33:30,920 --> 00:33:31,520
Next time.

628
00:33:32,400 --> 00:33:33,000
Next time.

629
00:34:09,960 --> 00:34:10,440
Xia Zhi.

630
00:34:13,639 --> 00:34:16,440
What's wrong? You lost your key of the house again?

631
00:34:18,739 --> 00:34:19,469
This time,

632
00:34:20,179 --> 00:34:21,840
it's not about losing the key.

633
00:34:25,110 --> 00:34:26,909
You have no money to pay the rent?

634
00:34:28,370 --> 00:34:30,830
Tell me how much you want to borrow this time.

635
00:34:41,750 --> 00:34:42,969
Xiao,

636
00:34:43,320 --> 00:34:45,250
I'm not borrowing money this time.

637
00:34:45,420 --> 00:34:46,480
I want to live here.

638
00:34:48,639 --> 00:34:49,330
Xiao,

639
00:34:49,360 --> 00:34:52,159
you must save me this time.

640
00:34:55,710 --> 00:34:57,060
I saved you every time.

641
00:34:57,440 --> 00:34:58,300
Just live here.

642
00:34:58,310 --> 00:35:00,570
But maybe you won't live here for so long.

643
00:35:02,650 --> 00:35:04,110
Are you moving elsewhere?

644
00:35:04,960 --> 00:35:06,060
It's a secret for now.

645
00:35:06,060 --> 00:35:07,370
But it should be fine for you to live here

646
00:35:07,370 --> 00:35:08,830
until you get your salary.

647
00:35:10,690 --> 00:35:12,730
Polly. You must be hungry.

648
00:35:22,660 --> 00:35:23,400
Actually,

649
00:35:25,320 --> 00:35:26,650
I think I've lost my job.

650
00:35:28,160 --> 00:35:29,490
You lost your job again?

651
00:35:31,120 --> 00:35:32,580
It's been two years since I graduated,

652
00:35:32,580 --> 00:35:33,970
and I've done seven jobs.

653
00:35:33,970 --> 00:35:35,570
Why didn't I get a stable job?

654
00:35:36,160 --> 00:35:37,530
It's only been two years since you graduated.

655
00:35:37,530 --> 00:35:38,930
It's normal to feel lost.

656
00:35:39,190 --> 00:35:41,510
Then why do you want to be a pilot?

657
00:35:42,090 --> 00:35:45,000
Maybe I think by being a pilot, I can have no constraint

658
00:35:45,000 --> 00:35:46,400
and have so much freedom.

659
00:35:48,140 --> 00:35:49,200
Who are you fooling?

660
00:35:49,200 --> 00:35:51,200
How can you say such a vulgar excuse?

661
00:35:51,480 --> 00:35:52,920
With your temper,

662
00:35:53,280 --> 00:35:54,540
who can constrain you?

663
00:35:56,080 --> 00:35:58,610
You have to keep all the promises you've made.

664
00:36:08,280 --> 00:36:10,140
When I viewed the recruitment website today,

665
00:36:10,140 --> 00:36:12,910
I've found that your company is conducting a social recruitment.

666
00:36:12,910 --> 00:36:16,140
Yes. The company has been reorganizing all the departments recently.

667
00:36:16,140 --> 00:36:17,900
I've been suffering from it.

668
00:36:20,840 --> 00:36:21,770
What do you think

669
00:36:22,100 --> 00:36:24,030
if I apply for a job in your company?

670
00:36:25,090 --> 00:36:26,500
You want to learn flying planes?

671
00:36:26,500 --> 00:36:27,630
I'm not that stupid.

672
00:36:30,350 --> 00:36:31,500
I mean

673
00:36:32,440 --> 00:36:33,560
I saw that how you were badly tortured

674
00:36:33,560 --> 00:36:34,760
while you were learning to fly planes.

675
00:36:34,760 --> 00:36:35,790
I won't learn it.

676
00:36:36,920 --> 00:36:37,880
So you are...

677
00:36:43,620 --> 00:36:44,450
Actually,

678
00:36:44,780 --> 00:36:47,240
I want to be a stewardess.

679
00:36:47,910 --> 00:36:48,840
Stewardess?

680
00:36:49,760 --> 00:36:51,670
They travel around the world for free,

681
00:36:51,670 --> 00:36:54,280
and check out all kinds of delicious food in the world.

682
00:36:54,280 --> 00:36:55,520
Enough, Ms. Xia Zhi.

683
00:36:55,520 --> 00:36:57,360
Don't cause trouble to the career of stewardess.

684
00:36:57,360 --> 00:36:58,890
What are you talking about?

685
00:36:59,870 --> 00:37:00,530
Is there

686
00:37:01,050 --> 00:37:02,120
any hope for me?

687
00:37:03,070 --> 00:37:05,730
Will you believe me if I tell you there's no hope?

688
00:37:05,740 --> 00:37:06,820
Okay, okay, okay.

689
00:37:07,530 --> 00:37:09,660
Alright. Give it a try if you want to do it.

690
00:37:09,660 --> 00:37:12,520
If it doesn't work, I'll support you economically.

691
00:37:16,450 --> 00:37:19,320
Alright. I'm going to send my resume.

692
00:38:41,280 --> 00:38:42,010
Mr. Nanting.

693
00:38:42,770 --> 00:38:44,280
We'll work under you from now on.

694
00:38:44,280 --> 00:38:46,210
I look forward to working with you.

695
00:38:47,240 --> 00:38:48,560
You're flattering him too early.

696
00:38:48,560 --> 00:38:49,890
He's talking still on the phone outside.

697
00:38:49,890 --> 00:38:50,850
He can't hear you.

698
00:38:50,850 --> 00:38:52,650
I'm just practising in advance.

699
00:38:59,830 --> 00:39:01,970
He has collected more models than me.

700
00:39:23,360 --> 00:39:26,340
Tomorrow, we'll arrange a trip to Luzhou Airlines' base in Australia

701
00:39:26,340 --> 00:39:28,640
to start the modification training of 787.

702
00:39:28,640 --> 00:39:29,240
Tomorrow?

703
00:39:29,280 --> 00:39:29,980
Tomorrow?

704
00:39:30,830 --> 00:39:31,640
So soon?

705
00:39:33,760 --> 00:39:34,840
I've sent the specifications

706
00:39:34,840 --> 00:39:36,360
of the modification to your email boxes.

707
00:39:36,360 --> 00:39:37,600
You must memorize them all.

708
00:39:37,600 --> 00:39:39,090
Go back and get ready.

709
00:39:40,560 --> 00:39:41,560
Thank you, Mr. Gu.

710
00:39:47,760 --> 00:39:48,490
Mr. Nanting,

711
00:39:48,810 --> 00:39:50,920
I look forward to working with you

712
00:39:59,450 --> 00:40:00,290
The door is still open.

713
00:40:00,290 --> 00:40:01,690
No need to close the door.

714
00:40:05,370 --> 00:40:08,180
[Middle Conference Room]

715
00:40:05,370 --> 00:40:08,180
[Interview for Flight Attendants]

716
00:40:07,440 --> 00:40:10,080
Please confirm your resumes again.

717
00:40:10,960 --> 00:40:12,760
Tidy up your appearances.

718
00:40:12,870 --> 00:40:15,220
Put away the shattered hair on the sides.

719
00:40:15,790 --> 00:40:17,900
Don't be nervous when you go in.

720
00:40:36,880 --> 00:40:37,520
I'm sorry.

721
00:40:37,960 --> 00:40:38,560
Sorry.

722
00:41:02,880 --> 00:41:04,010
I'll be my turn soon.

723
00:41:14,400 --> 00:41:15,130
Be careful.

724
00:41:42,900 --> 00:41:44,230
45 degrees to the right.

725
00:41:48,350 --> 00:41:51,130
[Liang Yueru, Luzhou Airlines]

726
00:41:48,350 --> 00:41:51,130
[Chief of the Cabin Department of Luzhou Airlines]

727
00:41:48,400 --> 00:41:49,200
Smile.

728
00:41:52,360 --> 00:41:53,210
Grin.

729
00:41:55,240 --> 00:41:56,570
45 degrees to the right.

730
00:41:58,070 --> 00:41:58,810
Turn right.

731
00:42:02,400 --> 00:42:05,250
[Ai Jia, Luzhou Airlines]

732
00:42:02,400 --> 00:42:05,250
[Cabin Department, Manager of Division One]

733
00:42:02,400 --> 00:42:05,250
[Director of the Cabin, Class A Instructor]

734
00:42:05,070 --> 00:42:05,840
Turn back.

735
00:42:09,400 --> 00:42:10,210
Li Yuheng.

736
00:42:13,400 --> 00:42:15,100
You graduated with a master's degree.

737
00:42:15,100 --> 00:42:16,320
You're very highly educated.

738
00:42:16,320 --> 00:42:18,240
Why do you want to be a flight attendant?

739
00:42:18,240 --> 00:42:19,480
I like taking plane.

740
00:42:19,800 --> 00:42:22,360
Every time I see flight attendants, I admire them.

741
00:42:22,360 --> 00:42:23,320
A flight attendant's smile

742
00:42:23,320 --> 00:42:24,960
can make the travelers, who have got tired from the journey,

743
00:42:24,960 --> 00:42:25,880
feel warm.

744
00:42:26,490 --> 00:42:28,800
So I want to be an excellent flight attendant,

745
00:42:28,800 --> 00:42:30,130
and pass out the warmth.

746
00:42:30,520 --> 00:42:31,780
As a flight attendant,

747
00:42:31,800 --> 00:42:33,420
if a passenger chats with you

748
00:42:33,720 --> 00:42:34,540
and invites you

749
00:42:34,540 --> 00:42:36,400
to travel with him after landing.

750
00:42:36,760 --> 00:42:37,760
What will you say?

751
00:42:37,760 --> 00:42:39,000
Thank you for your kindness.

752
00:42:39,000 --> 00:42:39,800
After landing,

753
00:42:39,800 --> 00:42:41,680
we have uniform arrangements for the work.

754
00:42:41,680 --> 00:42:43,060
It may not be convenient.

755
00:42:43,060 --> 00:42:45,300
Do you need other services

756
00:42:45,440 --> 00:42:46,920
or tea and drinks?

757
00:42:48,040 --> 00:42:49,230
Okay. Thank you.

758
00:42:51,880 --> 00:42:52,490
Next.

759
00:42:53,080 --> 00:42:53,720
Xia Zhi.
